<main>
	<!-- Subscriptions start -->
	<div class="subscriptions_section mb-5">
			<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://qureskincaredns.com/assets/css/_subscription_page.css">
			<div class="container mt-5">
					<div class="subscriptions_header text-center">
							<h1 class="subscription_subheadline mb-lg-5 mb-4">Subscriptions</h1>
							<p class="subscription_subtext mb-lg-5 mb-4">Consistency is key when it comes to skincare. Save with
									subscriptions and see long lasting results. </p>
							<p class="subscription_subtext">No hassle. Pause, cancel, and re-activate anytime.* </p>
					</div>

					<div class="subscriptions_content border-bottom mb-4">
							<p class="mb-4">Please carefully read this <strong>Subscriptions Policy</strong> prior to making a
									purchase. We want
									you to be completely satisfied with your online purchase.</p>
							<p class="mb-4">In taking up this special offer, you have agreed to the following terms and
									conditions:</p>
							<p class="mb-4">Opt for the subscription payment choice available on the product page. The specified
									delivery frequency is indicated on the same page. Your subscription starts as soon as your
									initial payment is processed.</p>
							<p class="mb-4">We will automatically debit the order amount on the same day of the month until
									cancelled by you (please see full terms and conditions here), and your order will be processed
									and sent out within the next 2 business days after each payment has been received</p>
							<p class="mb-4">Product Subscription items will ship automatically until you cancel. By placing a
									subscription order, you are authorizing us to charge your card for future orders at the
									frequency and quantity you selected. The actual cost of each shipment may vary depending on the
									quantity and frequency chosen.</p>
							<p class="mb-4">
									If your credit or debit card cannot be charged for any reason, we will attempt to charge your
									account two more times. Should this fail as well, you will not receive the box for that
									subscription period. Subscriptions can be cancelled a minimum of one week prior to billing date
									via email <a href="mailto:support@qureskincare.com">support@qureskincare.com</a> </p>
							<p class="mb-4">Cancellations after this time frame will still be billed for the subsequent period
									and the subscription item will be sent</p>
					</div>

					<div class="cancel_section border-bottom mb-4">
							<h6>Cancellations</h6>
							<p class="my-4">
									If you move, please email us at <a href="mailto:support@qureskincare.com">support@qureskincare.com</a> providing us with your full name,
									email, contact number, account number and new address. Failure to do is 7 days prior to dispatch
									might result in a re-ship fee if the item is shipped to the old address and is RTS. 
							</p>
					</div>

					<div class="cancel_section border-bottom mb-4">
							<h6>Change of address</h6>
							<p class="my-4">
									If you move, please email us at <a href="mailto:support@qureskincare.com">support@qureskincare.com</a> providing us with your full name,
									email, contact number, account number and new address. Failure to do is 7 days prior to dispatch
									might result in a re-ship fee if the item is shipped to the old address and is RTS. 
							</p>
					</div>

					<div class="cancel_section border-bottom mb-4">
							<h6>Promotional code</h6>
							<p class="my-4">
									If you move, please email us at <a href="mailto:support@qureskincare.com">support@qureskincare.com</a> providing us with your full name,
									email, contact number, account number and new address. Failure to do is 7 days prior to dispatch
									might result in a re-ship fee if the item is shipped to the old address and is RTS. 
							</p>
					</div>

					<div class="cancel_section">
							<h6>Order and delivery issues</h6>
							<p class="my-4">
									If your shipment is incorrect or damaged, or goes missing, simply email us at
									<a href="mailto:support@qureskincare.com">support@qureskincare.com</a> as soon as possible and we’ll do our best to help solve the issue right
									away for you!
							</p>
							<p>If you haven’t received your products but tracking says it’s delivered, start by asking family
									members and neighbors if they picked it up. Then check with the shipping carrier. If you still
									haven’t received your product 10 days after the scheduled delivery, email us at
									<a href="mailto:support@qureskincare.com">support@qureskincare.com</a> to let us know and handle it as soon as possible. </p>
					</div>
			</div>
	</div>
